      <h1>Jobs</h1>
                    <div class="image">
          <img src="/images/5qtac7xtiu5.jpg" alt="">
        </div>
            <p>We&rsquo;re always looking for talented individuals that strengthen our team. If you're creative, driven, and want to help build great software, please reach out to us!</p>
<p>Resumes can be sent to <a href="mailto:jobs@intelligentbits.com">jobs@intelligentbits.com</a>.</p>      <div class="clear"></div>
      
              
                
        <div class="job">
          <h2>Software Engineer (3+ years experience)</h2>
          
          <p>We are seeking an <span style="text-decoration: underline;">experienced</span> software engineer to join our small programming team! We're agile, and energetic, and growing into a nationally recognized transportation software company. Come help us write excellent software.</p>
<p><strong>Qualifications:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>C# .Net experience (3+ years required)</li>
<li>SQL Server and/or MySQL (3+ years preferred)</li>
<li>Strong problem solving skills</li>
<li>ASP.Net, JavaScript, AJAX, SOAP exposure a plus</li>
<li>Background in Android app development a plus</li>
<li>Cloud application development a plus</li>
<li>BS/BA in Computer Science/Computer Engineering required</li>
</ul>          
                      <div class="hidden">
              <p><strong>What makes BiTS great to work for?</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>You <span style="text-decoration: underline;">WILL</span> have a significant impact on the growth of the company</li>
<li>The high energy, high intensity culture.&nbsp; We are passionate about what we do</li>
<li>The work is challenging and fun; never a dull day</li>
<li>Located in downtown Buffalo.&nbsp; Our office is a short walk from some of the best food, entertainment, and sports in WNY</li>
<li>Paid parking in a covered garage in the middle of downtown Buffalo</li>
<li>Health Insurance, 401K, PTO</li>
</ul>
<p>Are you a quick learner, <span style="text-decoration: underline;">detail-oriented</span>, and self-motivated? Are you passionate about the code you write, eager to learn, and bring innovative ideas&nbsp;to the table? If you are excited to work in small, tight-knit team, learn a lot of technologies, and further your career within a fast growing company, please apply.</p>
<p>Local hire, full-time, benefits, salary based on experience.</p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 0px;">Required experience:</p>
<ul>
<li>Software Development: 3 years</li>
</ul>
<p style="margin-bottom: 0px;">Required education:</p>
<ul>
<li>BS/BA in Computer Science/Computer Engineering</li>
</ul>            </div>
