        <div class="job">
          <h2>Help Desk/Support Representative</h2>
          
          <p>We're known for our customer service. Help support our products keep our customers happy!</p>
<p><strong>Duties:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Support&nbsp;customers via incoming support calls, emails, and live chats</li>
<li>Learn our products&nbsp;to answer all questions related to&nbsp;software usage</li>
<li>Help create software tutorials for common questions and issues</li>
<li>Administer training sessions with new customers</li>
</ul>          
                      <div class="hidden">
              <p><strong>Qualifications:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Organization and multi-tasking skills</li>
<li>Phone skills: comfortable calling clients/users</li>
<li>An appreciation for grammar/professional writing</li>
<li>Willingness to learn new software and a new industry</li>
<li>Passion for quality customer service</li>
<li>Some experience with Microsoft Excel, Word, and Outlook</li>
<li>The ability to identify user error versus a software defect (bug)</li>
<li>Quick learner</li>
</ul>
<p>Offices located in downtown Buffalo. Background in customer service very important. This is a full-time position with benefits.</p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 0px;">Required experience:</p>
<ul>
<li>Customer Service: 2 years</li>
</ul>
<p style="margin-bottom: 0px;">Required education:</p>
<ul>
<li>Associate's</li>
</ul>            </div>
