        <div class="job">
          <h2>Marketing, Editor, and Sales Administrator</h2>
          
          <p>We are seaking a motivated and detail-oriented individual to join our team and help us promote our products, via direct mailer, social media, and email campaigns.</p>
<p><strong>Duties:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Write news articles for company website and promote on social media</li>
<li>Proofread internal/external support articles, sales materials, and procedures</li>
<li>Help design intuitive software tutorials</li>
<li>Work with external design firm on website changes and marketing pieces</li>
<li>Help sales team design and&nbsp;administer regular marketing campaigns</li>
<li>Plan for tradeshows</li>
<li>Keep our sales staff organized!</li>
</ul>          
                      <div class="hidden">
              <p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Strong business writing and editing skills</li>
<li>2+ years of professional writing experience</li>
<li>An eye for detail and aesthetics</li>
<li>Delivers consistent, high-quality work</li>
<li>Willingness to learn new software and a new industry</li>
<li>Experience with Microsoft Excel, Word, Outlook</li>
<li>Basic understanding of&nbsp;HTML</li>
<li>Ability to adapt and learn quickly</li>
</ul>
<p>Offices located in downtown Buffalo. Local candidtates only.</p>
<p>Job Type: Full-time</p>            </div>
